    "7323517": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Nasejuna",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's see... Next, we just need to put the Kory Drums back in their original places before performing the piece according to the scores on the stone walls, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Rashnu will definitely be happy to answer us when she hears her favorite music."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Do excuse my presumption, but the ritual that bound the Order of Skeptics to the Pari is one of great significance..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "I think that it would only be proper Order of Skeptics regulation if its Vijnanapati — that is to say myself — were to preside over it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? But we were the ones who got all the five Kory Drums!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Even if you are Lady Sorush's Yasnapati, I believe this to be out of line... or should I call this prideful presumption upon her favor?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Lady Sorush is Khvarena's Envoy. She might have behaved more amicably to the two of you on account of your aid in fulfilling her destined mission..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Yet this is but a manifestation of her virtue, and not any credit of yours. Do not forget your place. Give praise and stand in awe of her every action, as you should."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, that's what you say... But even though Sorush always acts all high and mighty, Paimon doesn't think she's all that great... or that distant from us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "That does not sound like something that shall be written into a hymn of praise."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, I'd say it's praise enough by Paimon's standards."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "#Well, what about you, then, {NICKNAME}? Do you desire... Do you want to play the Kory Drums and awaken the familiar of Barsom for me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Eh, Nasejuna can do it. Being a bystander's alright. Sometimes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Ah, a sensible person, I see. After all, such an important ritual should indeed be left in the hands of one who understands our traditions the most, and who occupies a most suitable position..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Silence! I did tell you before that a Pari's word is final. Doubt not my judgment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "...As you will."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, I propose to give you, and no one else, this honorable task. Do you accept?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You need not speak in such a winding manner, Sorush."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#That's right! If you want to ask {NICKNAME} for help, just say \"I'll leave it to you\" or something. No need for all this weird talk!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "This is not \"weird talk.\" These are words that befit a Pari's stature. Well then. I shall take that as your acquiesence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm not a bad performer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Exactly. Cooking, combat, errands, espionage, we can do it all! This is definitely way easier than extinguishing the Sign of Apaosha — we're not gonna trip up here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "And yet adventurers you remain, rough folk of the outdoors. It would be best if I handle such critical matters related to our history and tradition as this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "#Nasuraia. {M#He}{F#She} is the Yasnapati I have chosen, and now {M#he}{F#she} willingly serves. Will you bar our path?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "I... I have no reason to doubt your decisions, astute as they are..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "#Then it is concluded. Speak no more. Come, {NICKNAME}. This momentous task is yours."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't you worry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Oh, I have no fear. You are my Yasnapati, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Well if you say so, Sorush, then leave this to us! Just relax, Nasejuna. We know the Kory Drums are very important. {NICKNAME}'s not going to ruin them or anything!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
