    "7323206": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Sorush",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "C'mon, Sorush, wake up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Agh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew, you're finally awake! You really scared Paimon, fainting like you did up there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "I... I'm fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But the tree opened up after that, and we followed the path in. This is... the giant lotus, Gaokerena, that Zurvan was talking about, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What happened to you earlier? Did something go wrong with the Chaplet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "I saw memories that the earth returned to the Harvisptokhm. Countless Pari, Dahrian machines, and human warriors sacrificed themselves in battle against the demons."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "A masked swordsman, a one-armed sage, and our ancient forerunners defeated the monsters that rose from the depths."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Their consciousnesses then joined the Harvisptokhm together with the Khvarena, turning into rain that descended from the heavens."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Dahrian machines... Wait, did things really go the way Nasejuna said they did?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Looks like we'll have to ask Zurvan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah. But what should we do now? Paimon remembers Zurvan saying that we needed to clean out the impurities, or something like that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "We must enter the Defiled Chambers within our god's consciousness to rescue the Spenta Hearts trapped inside the impurities. Only then will the consciousness reawaken."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "In the memories I saw, that place was a boundless void."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If that's the case, how are we supposed to get in?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Come with me. We only need to follow the paths left by the heroes of old, and we will reach our destination."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
