    "7323224": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Sorush",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Spenta Hearts here have all been brought back to the lotus. According to what you said earlier, Sorush, we should be able to awaken the divine consciousness now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "In that case, let the real Rite of Ab-Zohr begin."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Next, I shall borrow the power of Khvarena to make the Flower of Sanctity bloom once again within Gaokerena."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "But this will mean unleashing the filth gathered within the sacred lotus, which will transform into monsters that bar our path."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "It matters not, for so long as the god's consciousness is awakened, the power of the Amrita will defend us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "If the Flower of Sanctity grows, it will spread Amrita all over the land, and cleanse all its impurities."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "This, then, is a final battle worthy of a Bloomguard!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
