    "7325623": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Nasejuna",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Great Envoy, and her honored Yasnapati, I fear that this is as far as I may attend you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And what's the problem this time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "According to the texts, the road ahead is full of perils that no ordinary mortal may bear."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Once we go in here, we shall be within the proving ground that the Dahrians once used to test their machines. There is even an incomplete prototype of a giant machine amongst them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "The copied Dahrian records in my notes say that this place was once modified for use as fortifications from which the monsters could be attacked, although it didn't see much use in that regard."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Strange, isn't it? Why would the Dahrians, who triggered the defiling disaster, create machines to fight monsters?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "All the same, now that we have activated the control systems for these ruins, the defensive mechanisms within the proving ground must also have been activated."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "The Great Song we are searching for should be within that Golem. Though I am stymied, I suspect that it will prove easy for you all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "Please allow me to stay here and await your return, so that we may be able to obtain all the Great Songs of Khvarena."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sorush",
                    "T": "Well, you are indeed but a mere human. Such a request is to be expected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nasejuna",
                    "T": "By your gracious leave, then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, guess Nasejuna's slipping off at the last moment. Still, Paimon's a lot happier now that the two of you won't be bouncing off each other for a while..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
